---
description: Run the test suite after substantive tracker or API changes
globs: src/lib/**,src/db/**,src/app/api/**
alwaysApply: false
---

After editing files under `src/lib/`, `src/db/`, or `src/app/api/`, run:

```bash
npm run test
```

If you changed TypeScript/React surface area broadly, also run `npm run lint` before finishing.
